source.name: Soybase
source.description: SoyBase is the USDA-ARS soybean genetics and genomics database. Contents include the genome sequence, the genetic map (markers, QTL, etc.), metabolic pathways, transcription and expression data, mutant information, and selected analysis tools and community resources.
